    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1869-11-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1869-11-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="506"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d506">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Field</persName>, Assistant
                        Attorney-General, to Mr. <persName type="to">Phelps</persName>, assistant
                        district attorney.</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of Justice</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-11-23">
                        <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 23, 1869</date>.</dateline>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">
                        <seg type="margin">[188]</seg> *[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Benj. K. Phelps</hi>,<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Assistant United States Attorney, New Yorlc City:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Go to Raleigh; oppose bonding of steamer Hornet and all recognition by the court
                    of any “republic of Cuba.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>W. A. FIELD,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Assistant Attorney-General.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
